Subject: Inefficient disk usage post-upgrade
Description: We updated to 5.9.4.0 last week and since then the server seems to only be saving to the core 20GB drive rather than our expanded 170GB storage and the UI is consistently locking up when attempting to offload logs and shadow files.  Shadow filing also appears to be acting strangely following this upgrade but it'd be easier to describe on a call.
Solution_Comment__c: cleared the system disk space and provided information on how the new system for file shadowing works.
